    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选 特斯拉粉丝全力支持推动 3000 亿美元反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/tesla-tsla-devotees-go-all-in-driving-300-billion-rally-on-trump-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普当选总统让特斯拉公司的粉丝们重新振作起来。随着投资者纷纷买入特斯拉股票，特斯拉股价似乎势不可挡，他们相信特朗普连任将给这家由埃隆·马斯克领导的电动汽车制造商带来意外之财。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/tesla-tsla-devotees-go-all-in-driving-300-billion-rally-on-trump-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 19:11:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Onex 股价飙升至创纪录水平，此前道明银行已将其评级从“中性”下调至“中性”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/onex-rises-after-shedding-lone-neutral-rating-with-td-upgrade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大投资公司 Onex Corp. 放弃了唯一的卖方中性评级，随后其股价跃升至历史新高。由于今年该公司进行了大规模信贷融资，TD Cowen 将该股评级提升至买入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/onex-rises-after-shedding-lone-neutral-rating-with-td-upgrade</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 17:26:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
